  "time_ut": 1656931756,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0d87\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dc0\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0db4\u0dcf \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "While the child is in the womb, the mother's neck is cut and the gold necklace is stolen",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Polpithigama Police reported a sad news of a mother who was walking home with a child in her hand, who was killed by cutting her throat with a sharp weapon and then breaking the gold necklace tied around her neck.",
        "Police say that a 35-year-old woman resident of Irudeniya, Tholambuela area has been killed.",
        "The victim's husband works in the North-West Canal project and he encountered this incident while returning home from Polpithigama town in the morning.",
        "The police say that she was carrying her one and a half year old child at the time of the murder.",
        "The police say that she identified the suspect who was wearing a mask when the necklace was broken from her neck in Irudeniya Tholambuala area, and information is revealed that the suspect cut his throat and ran away to escape the robbery.",
        "According to the hospital sources, the child screamed along with this incident and the victim was taken to the hospital after hearing the sound.",
        "Police say that the suspect who has committed this crime and fled after breaking the gold necklace has been identified, so they have started an operation to arrest him."
      ],
